this i a python project.
It has two scripts the send.py and the recieve.py 
this two scripts implement file transfar protocol in python

the recieve script acts as the server waiting for new connection 
and whenever one is detected it ges ready to recieve files 

the send.py script on the othe hand acts as the client that trys to 
connect to the serer this case recieve.py script at run time. 

if the server is up and running the connetion is established and the client or send 
module is ready to share files  else connection fails the client crushes 
